Join Us


Motorola Solutions creates innovative, mission-critical communication solutions and services that help public safety and commercial customers build safer cities and thriving communities. 

Founded in 1928, Motorola has a history of innovation that has revolutionized communications. From pioneering mobile communications in the 1930s and making equipment that carried the first words from the moon in 1969, to supporting modern-day emergency response equipment for disaster relief efforts around the world, Motorola Solutions has a global footprint with products that demonstrate its thought leadership.









 

              Our employees enable industries worldwide to thrive, achieve and do   their best work. They create indispensable, indestructible tools to help   more people in more businesses in more places to be their best. They do   it to better serve the government, health, public safety and other businesses for which we've created clear and confident communications   solutions for more than 80 years. The work they do is meaningful, impactful and ongoing.










AND WE NEED DRIVEN, MOTIVATED VISIONARIES LIKE YOU TO JOIN  THEM.


Meet the leaders of our present and future. Then join us.









OUR VALUES




we areinnovative
We constantly create ingenious solutions to the real challenges of today, tomorrow and beyond.



we arepassionate
We meet every challenge with energy and determination, always pursuing ever-higher standards.



we aredriven
We keep it simple by focusing on what matters most so we can seize opportunities with speed and confidence.



we areaccountable
We stand behind the work we do, the contributions we make and the high business standards we maintain.



we arepartners
We succeed together because we respect all individuals and value contributions from colleagues and customers alike.





To work with and for Motorola Solutions, start here. Our Values are based on a foundation of uncompromising integrity and ethics that influence everything we do. They represent not just what we believe, but how we will behave toward each other, our customers, our suppliers and all of our stakeholders.








Valuing an Inclusive Environment


By focusing on our Values, Motorola Solutions strives to create an inclusive environment where every individual has opportunity to make an impact. That's how we build on the innovation that has been our legacy for more than 80 years. It all starts with our belief that the next big idea can come from anyone, anywhere, at any time. At Motorola Solutions, diversity and inclusiveness are more than the keys to meeting and exceeding our customers' diverse needs - they're our competitive advantage.

Motorola Solutions is a smaller, more focused company than our predecessor, Motorola, Inc., allowing each of our employees greater say and greater impact. But our culture also asks every one of us to contribute to our fullest potential. With our Values as our foundation, we strive to engage the organization in promoting a culture that values diversity of thought. This gives each of us the chance to contribute to the best of our ability, and is the driving force behind Motorola Solutions' success.










Motorola's Business Councils Welcome You To Be Your Best


Everything you'll do at Motorola will be with the support of the top minds, tools and various Motorola Business Councils behind you. It's how we connect a range of abilities and ideas within the organization to the progress we're making outside of it. As we begin our new chapter as Motorola Solutions, our Business Councils are excited to shape their missions to support and grow our new business strategies.

Bring your perspective to Motorola Solutions and see what - and whom - you might shape. 

GIVE YOURSELF THE OPPORTUNITY TO SEE HOW FAR YOU CAN GO. 

Motorola Solutions is an Equal Opportunity Employer committed to no discrimination because of race, color, creed, marital status, age, religion, sex, national origin, citizenship, sexual orientation, gender identity or expression, genetic information, disability, protected veteran, or any other legally protected characteristic.










Saving the Day with Best In Class Solutions


Motorola Solutions connects people through technology. Public safety and commercial customers around the world turn to Motorola Solutions innovations when they want highly connected teams that have the information they need throughout their workdays and in the moments that matter most to them.

Our customers rely on us for the expertise, services and solutions we provide, trusting our years of invention and innovation experience. By partnering with customers and observing how our products can help in their specific industries, we are able to enhance our customers' experience every day.









 

 

            Taking great ideas from concept to reality is what innovative companies   do. At Motorola Solutions, we believe true innovation occurs when a new   technology solves a problem customers didn't know they had or in a way   they never thought possible. We strive to deliver solutions that bring   the right information, to the right person, at the right time. We help   our customers be their best in the moments that matter most —  protecting citizens, connecting with shoppers and empowering IT operations.

                  To read about how we're mobilizing businesses and lives around the globe, view our most recent press releases and case studies.







Corporate Responsibility


HELPING THE WORLD BE ITS BEST 
At Motorola Solutions, we are good citizens by design. Through the   solutions you'll create here, you'll help Motorola Solutions live out   our mission of helping people be their best, creating economic   opportunities and growth in the regions where we do business. 

  Our   products, services, operations, offices and factories are   environmentally conscious. Our commitment to doing the right thing   extends to our global supply chain through auditing and training. We set   expectations for our suppliers and work with them to conduct their   operations fairly and with human decency. We invest in the communities   where we operate through charitable giving and by expanding access to technologies. And we encourage our employees to push the boundaries of eco-innovation.













Helping the world be at its best includes helping employees be their best in all they do. Our employees embody the high value we place on doing business lawfully and ethically everywhere. See our latest Corporate Responsibility Report to learn how Motorola Solutions is approaching the future with mindfulness and balance.
See our Latest Corporate Responsibility Report

















CULTURE


A Culture Where the Best Thrive


                At Motorola Solutions, you'll find a culture of people striving to be their best. A culture focused not on manufacturing products, but on solving problems that allow customers and businesses to thrive.
You will:

Invent first-ever solutions.
Connect customers to ideas they can't live without and have never experienced before.
Solve pressing problems with solutions that come uniquely from the collaboration taking place here.








EXPERIENCE MOTOROLA SOLUTIONS


To experience what it's like to work at Motorola Solutions, view some of our latest press releases.
 
Or just Apply.













INNOVATE FOR GOOD

                We look for the most advanced problems solvers - like you - to help us create technologies that rise to the challenges of governments and public safety customers worldwide. To connect firemen to policemen to emergency responders to nurses to specialists to lives saved. To protect communities, grow businesses and make work safer and more efficient. To reduce costs while increasing dialogue, opportunity and growth.
 
Working with us is a chance to innovate for good.
 
Discover the innovative spirit that has kept both our customers and our employees satisfied for more than 80 years. Then join us.
            






