Why Motorola Solutions


Connect With Life-Changing Opportunities
Make an impact. Be inspired. Emerge a leader. 

  You'll   take on much more than a job at Motorola Solutions, because the work we   do is literally life-changing for people and businesses around the   world. It's a focus that relies on your passion, potential and that   great stuff no one even knows you have. 

  Here, you'll get   recognized fast for your talents and be supported with the education,   resources and visibility you're looking for. The really good   opportunities you can't get just anywhere. 

  Right now, people all   over the world are counting on us. To answer their problems. To   energize and revitalize their businesses. To save their lives. To   connect them with the solutions we need you to think up.










