Programs and Opportunities


Seize Your Best Career Opportunity Right on Campus
Whether you're a current student looking for an   internship or are preparing to graduate, you'll take what you've learned   on campus even further in a career at Motorola Solutions: 

USE YOUR IDEAS TO HELP PEOPLE BE THEIR BEST.
INNOVATE FOR A GREENER FUTURE.WORK WITH THE BEST TEAMS ANYWHERE. 
FIND OUT HOW WE REWARD HARD WORK AND SMART IDEAS.
						             
							
								
							
							
						
						   
					









Internships and Co-Ops


Motorola Solutions participates in co-op and internship programs with select universities worldwide to offer you hands-on experience that will boost your resume and ignite your interests. You'll be treated as a junior professional with the opportunity to work alongside some of the most gifted telecommunications professionals around - solving real-life problems with solutions that enable people across all kinds of industries worldwide to thrive, achieve and do their best work.

Many of our students choose Motorola Solutions full-time when they graduate. For more information on your school's involvement in this program, please contact your co-op or internship placement office.










Graduating Students


Every year, Motorola actively recruits talented students to join our team upon graduation through university career fairs and the interviews we hold on-campus. The competition is stiff, but the experience is unmatched.
This is the career you've been hoping for: A challenging, supportive environment where you'll be listened to, respected and challenged to connect people around the world to better and smarter daily lives. In addition to a rewarding experience, you'll receive many great benefits.
Interested in innovating for the good of the world? Apply now.
















