Motorola Solutions

From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia


					Jump to:					navigation, 					search


Motorola Solutions, Inc.





Type

Public


Traded as
NYSE: MSI
S&P 500 Component


Industry
Telecommunications equipment


Predecessor
Motorola, Inc.


Founded
January 4, 2011; 6 years ago (January 4, 2011)


Headquarters
Chicago, Illinois, U.S.



Key people

